data.description: Welcome to your dream home on Pierce St!!Nestled near parks, Pierce Pool, and the DI School, this townhouse presents an ideal location for families and individuals alike. Imagine stepping outside your front door and being just moments away from lush green spaces, and marsh views where you can enjoy leisurely strolls, picnics, or outdoor activities.As you step inside this amazing townhouse, you'll be greeted by a open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living, dining, and updated kitchen area.. Upstairs you will find 3 great bedrooms including the owners suite which has tons of natural light and overlooks the back yard. Both baths were recently updated with new tile floors and showers.  Make an appointment now to see this fantastic townhome .
